## Medical Disclaimer

BloodMate is a software application designed to assist in blood bank management. 
This software is not intended to replace professional medical judgment or clinical 
decision-making. All medical decisions should be made by qualified healthcare 
professionals. The developers of BloodMate are not responsible for any medical 
outcomes resulting from the use of this software.

## Data Privacy Notice

This software may process sensitive medical data. Users are responsible for 
ensuring compliance with applicable data protection regulations including but 
not limited to HIPAA, GDPR, and local privacy laws. The developers recommend 
implementing appropriate security measures and obtaining necessary consents 
before processing personal health information.